text: The Denmark women's national cricket team represents Denmark in women's cricket. They were a Women's One Day International team from 1989 to 1999 and since 2018 they have played Women's Twenty20 Internationals. They have played in two Women's Cricket World Cup in 1993 and 1997. ==References== Category:National sports teams of Denmark Category:Cricket in Europe Category:Women's national cricket teams
